#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:22
msgid ""
"For making other changes to the geometry of editable objects, you should "
"use *Edit Mode*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/introduction.rst:24
msgid ""
